{"tid":966772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國女勇敢獨自旅遊印度　慘遭下藥性侵","createTime":"2019-01-03T05:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T13:08:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"618f7de414a320608bffad4c9c4151ab4638ac4b","tid":966772,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"中國貴州一名25歲女子相當勇敢，獨自前往印度中央邦旅遊，但在本周一向當地警方報案，指自己遭當地一群青年下藥性侵。<br />\n據中國《梨視頻》報導，女子報案指出，自己獨自前往印度旅遊，並在旅途中認識一群青年，更一度獲對方招待，大家開心吃吃喝喝。但隨後她喝下對方招待的飲料後，馬上失去意識，女子醒來後，認為自己遭到下藥性侵，於是報警處理。警方表示目前已經受理女子的報案，並對女子進行醫學檢測，全案也展開調查中。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3yKKo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3yKKo3.png&h=47b8ac66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vgouVvJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvgouVvJ.png&h=1353078e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"033c1a865c5714ef49ec6fdf1dce86cd18f6fea1","tid":966772,"uid":20066,"like":79,"dislike":8,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔係閪痕去印度做乜<br />\n女仔去得印度都預比人輪架啦"},{"pid":"a1737910fc5acf6b0f653975ede23e4debd3e181","tid":966772,"uid":157197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"可能專登去食咖哩佬"},{"pid":"5ee07df361d04a987ff8cfd974e259a43ab3beb4","tid":966772,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"有冇腦"},{"pid":"1afa07ec4986168bcd0eea7796d4e33b16589da6","tid":966772,"uid":146376,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"蠢就蠢啦 勇敢喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab912c9150c1779271e2434b34cdc6ed91e6d0c0","tid":966772,"uid":34013,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"印度佬姦人唔會落藥  有疑點唔信"},{"pid":"812ee3a9e3f549ff340a7d2dd1485fd79f20cc6f","tid":966772,"uid":280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci